        {
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 16,
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 1,
                "prefix": 1.0,
                "text": "BACKGROUND"
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 17,
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "prefix": 1.1,
                "text": "This document sets out the procedures to be followed by all Mid Essex Hospital Services NHS Trust (MEHT) staff who are involved with clinical research."
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 18,
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "prefix": 1.0,
                "text": "It aims to set out the information required to be added to EDGE (the Local Portfolio Management System used by MEHT as agreed with North Thames Clinical Research Network (CRN)) for each patient. Patient data is added to Edge to record recruitment activity, ensure follow up appointments occur at the right time points and to support timely invoicing."
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 19,
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "prefix": 1.3,
                "text": "Edge is a cloud-based research local portfolio management system used by MEHT to record patient data. Edge is used by MEHT, and the National Institute of Health Research (NIHR) CRN North Thames to correlate recruitment with accruals. MEHT are able to see all patient details, including identifiable data, however CRN North Thames can only see the number of patients recruited to a study. At no point is CRN North Thames able to see any patient identifiable data."
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 20,
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 1,
                "prefix": 2.0,
                "text": "PURPOSE"
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 21,
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "prefix": 2.1,
                "text": "This document describes the information required to be inputted onto Edge for each patient. It covers which fields should be completed."
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 22,
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "prefix": 2.2,
                "text": "The document aims to provide clear guidance on the information to be included on Edge for each patient."
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 23,
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "prefix": 2.3,
                "text": "The objective of Edge is to provide a good quality resource for members of the R&D Department and to improve the quality of research management."
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 24,
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 1,
                "prefix": 3.0,
                "text": "APPLICABLE TO"
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 25,
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "prefix": 3.1,
                "text": "Any Trust employee involved with clinical research including Research Managers, Research Nurses, Research Midwives, Allied Health Professionals, Trial Coordinators, Data Managers and members of the Research & Development department."
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 26,
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 1,
                "prefix": 4.0,
                "text": "RESPONSIBILITIES"
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 27,
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "prefix": 4.1,
                "text": "All research staff members working on research projects are responsible for adding and maintaining accurate up to date information on Edge.."
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 28,
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 1,
                "prefix": 5.0,
                "text": "PROCEDURE"
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 29,
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "prefix": 5.1,
                "text": "When adding a patient to Edge, the minimum dataset required should include:"
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 30,
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "text": "a) Name"
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 31,
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "text": "b) Date of Birth"
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 32,
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "text": "c) NHS No."
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 33,
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "text": "d) Hospital No."
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 34,
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "text": "e) Participant Type"
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 35,
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "text": "f) Consultant"
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 36,
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "prefix": 5.2,
                "text": "Once a patient has been consented to the study and randomised, the Randomisation No. should be completed on Edge."
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 37,
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "prefix": 5.3,
                "text": "If a patient declines to take part in a study or is ineligible, the off study box should be selected and the following information completed:"
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 38,
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "text": "a) Reason"
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 39,
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "text": "b) Decision"
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 40,
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "prefix": 5.4,
                "text": "Any relevant additional information should be included in the Comments box, to include, but not limited to, dates of follow-up telephone calls or questionnaires due dates. No clinical information should be included."
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 41,
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "prefix": 5.5,
                "text": "If an appointment has been made for the patient, the appointment tab should be completed to include:"
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 42,
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "text": "a) Subject"
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 43,
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "text": "b) Date"
            }
        },
        {
